OL,3,CCap to disability support funding put
OL,4,Cdozens of Jersey jobs at risk
OL,6,FDozens of people in Jersey who help
OL,7,Fthose living with disabilities to get
OL,8,Femployment are at risk of being made
OL,9,Fredundant themselves.
OL,11,FDue to a reduction in government
OL,12,Ffunding, the Jersey Employment Trust
OL,13,F(JET) said it must review the scale of
OL,14,Fits services.
OL,16,FThat could result in all 38 staff
OL,17,Fmembers being laid off.
