OL,3,CCap to disability support funding put
OL,4,Cdozens of Jersey jobs at risk
OL,6,FThe charity has been advised that
OL,7,Ffuture funding will be substantially
OL,8,Flower than required to maintain its
OL,9,Fcurrent level of clients and services.
OL,11,FJET says that while it continues to
OL,12,Fengage with the Government of Jersey,
OL,13,Fit must take "responsible steps" to
OL,14,Frealign its operations at EmployJersey
OL,15,F(JET) Ltd with the lower funding that
OL,16,Fis being made available.
OL,18,FITV News has contacted Jersey's
OL,19,Fgovernment for a response.
