OL,3,CCap to disability support funding put
OL,4,Cdozens of Jersey jobs at risk
OL,6,FThe JET is contracted by the
OL,7,FGovernment's Employment, Social
OL,8,FSecurity, and Housing Department,
OL,9,Fproviding #1.9 million worth of
OL,10,Fvocational training and employment
OL,11,Fsupport for islanders with
OL,12,Fdisabilities and long-term health
OL,13,Fconditions.
OL,15,FThe Trust's service has been costing
OL,16,Fmore due to increases in the cost of
OL,17,Fliving, with the body relying on an
OL,18,Fadditional #785,000 grant last year to
OL,19,Fkeep operating.
