OL,3,CCap to disability support funding put
OL,4,Cdozens of Jersey jobs at risk
OL,6,FIn a statement, the JET says: "It is
OL,7,Flikely that the Trust will need to
OL,8,Frefer more than half of the 550
OL,9,Fclients it supports each year to the
OL,10,FGovernment to stay within the #1.9
OL,11,Fmillion grant.
OL,13,F"It will also now close its waiting
OL,14,Flist of more than 50 Islanders, and
OL,15,Fpause the acceptance of any new
OL,16,Freferrals, including any school
OL,17,Fleavers this summer.
