OL,3,CCap to disability support funding put
OL,4,Cdozens of Jersey jobs at risk
OL,6,F"No final decisions have yet been made
OL,7,Fon individual roles within the
OL,8,Forganisation, and the consultation
OL,9,Fprocess is intended to explore all
OL,10,Foptions, including ways to minimise
OL,11,Fcompulsory redundancies where possible.
OL,13,F"Staff at Acorn Enterprises, which is
OL,14,Fa separate company under the umbrella
OL,15,Fof JET, are unaffected.
