OL,3,CCap to disability support funding put
OL,4,Cdozens of Jersey jobs at risk
OL,6,F"The JET recognises the seriousness of
OL,7,Fthis situation and the concern it will
OL,8,Fcause for staff, clients and their
OL,9,Ffamilies. Supporting those affected
OL,10,Fand communicating clearly and
OL,11,Fcompassionately remains a priority,
OL,12,Fand all clients are in the process of
OL,13,Fbeing contacted over the coming days.
OL,15,F"The Trust will provide further
OL,16,Fupdates as the consultation process
OL,17,Fprogresses and, while that is getting
OL,18,Funderway, will not be providing
OL,19,Ffurther comment at this time."
